<tr><td>It is/was + focus + that/who + rest of clause</td><td>cleft sentence (it)</td><td>It was Tom who broke the window.</td></tr>
<tr><td>What + clause + is/was + focus</td><td>cleft sentence (what)</td><td>What I need is a holiday.</td></tr>
